[all shouting, grunting]

01:42.686 --> 01:44.478
[grunting]

01:46.065 --> 01:48.524
[yelling]

01:48.526 --> 01:51.026
[growling]

01:51.028 --> 01:52.694
[grunting]

01:52.696 --> 01:56.156
Well, bart, you've really
wet the mogwai this time.

01:56.158 --> 01:58.534
