02:07.795 --> 02:09.545
Hey, ralph did find that polyp.

02:09.547 --> 02:11.004
It was benign.

02:11.006 --> 02:12.965
Unlike your punishment.

02:12.967 --> 02:15.592
Fine, don't believe me.
No one ever believes me.

02:15.594 --> 02:17.094
Do your worst.

02:17.096 --> 02:20.514
