-Mm-hmm, they'll do that.
-[phone chimes]

02:40.744 --> 02:42.369
Oh.

02:42.371 --> 02:45.080
Homer, we just got invited
to a wedding...

02:45.082 --> 02:47.207
In the poconos.

02:47.209 --> 02:49.585
It's a destination wedding.

02:49.587 --> 02:51.962
