has a...

03:18.657 --> 03:20.657
[gags] cucumber in it.

03:20.659 --> 03:22.659
And this one's in the poconos,

03:22.661 --> 03:26.830
Which sounds like islands,
but it's just pennsylvania.

03:26.832 --> 03:29.166
And you're forced to do
all these

03:29.168 --> 03:30.959
