to be happy?

19:10.358 --> 19:12.233
[grunts] I do!

19:12.235 --> 19:13.901
This girl doesn't love you.

19:13.903 --> 19:15.987
Her family only brought you here

19:15.989 --> 19:17.864
For your peat sniffing.

19:17.866 --> 19:21.701
Pa, hamish, owen,
