19:21.703 --> 19:23.286
Of course it's true.

19:23.288 --> 19:25.163
You're just a nose to us.

19:25.165 --> 19:26.998
We've got to compete with

19:27.000 --> 19:29.458
All these celebrity
booze brands.

19:29.460 --> 19:32.545
From your tall, dark clooneys
to your wee danny devitos,

19:32.547 --> 19:36.215
There's no room for a passable
entry-level scotch.

19:36.217 --> 19:39.260
William, I didn't know about
