19:39.262 --> 19:42.930
I swear, I'd love you
even if you never sniffed

19:42.932 --> 19:45.266
Another bog
as long as you lived.

19:45.268 --> 19:47.852
I wish I could believe you.

19:47.854 --> 19:49.562
I'll prove it.

19:50.607 --> 19:51.731
-[shouts]
-[pained groan]

19:51.733 --> 19:53.191
